channel.description:
[center][img]http://i55.tinypic.com/20z7drt.jpg[/img][/center] [hr] Hello, I am "Synergy" and I am developing a server with my friend, Uncalled. The server 317, loading 562; we currently have Primal, Korasi's Sword [under development], Statius, etc. This server is going to turn out to be spectacular! I can't wait to see the outcome of it all, once we work on it for a few weeks to months, the server's going to be near perfect to how I want it. Me and Uncalled will be working on this for hours each day, everyday. Once we've got this in our grips we'll have the best server there is! [hr] [b]Goals:[/b]
[ul][li]Perfected Dungeoneering.[/li] [li]Clipped following[/li] [li]Perfect P.K.[/li] [li]N.P.C. clipping[/li] [li]Perfected models[/li] [li]Two worlds[/li] [li]Castle Wars[/li] [li]Clan Wars[/li] [li]Barbarian Assault[/li][/ul]
[hr] [b]Staff:[/b]
[ul][li][b]Synergy (me) - Coder & Owner[/b][/li] [li][b]Uncalled - Main coder[/b][/li][/ul]
